{"ID":"20230723225722-ueqval4","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20230723225722-ueqval4","scroll":"\u0026#123;\u0026quot;rootId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230723225722-ueqval4\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;startId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230723225807-p7ga18l\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;endId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230723225722-n22nfgw\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;scrollTop\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230723225722-n22nfgw\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;focusStart\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusEnd\u0026quot;:0\u0026#125;","title":"2.2 TCP IP 的网络接口层的相关协议","updated":"20230723225844"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230723225807-p7ga18l","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-p7ga18l","updated":"20230723225825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2.1 广域网使用的设备"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-epuv0f8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-epuv0f8","updated":"20230723225807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 传统电话拨号连接：通过PPP协议"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-7u91mgj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-7u91mgj","updated":"20230723225829"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早期网络大概都只能通过调制解调器加上电话线以及计算机的九针串行端口，然后通过Point-to-Point Protocol (PPP协议) 配合拨号程序来取得网络IP参数，这样就可以上网了。因为PPP支持TCP/IP、NetBEUI、IPX/SPX等通信协议、所以使用度非常广"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-7hh0142","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-7hh0142","updated":"20230723225807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.整合服务数字网络 Integrated Services Digital Network ISDK"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-0if97e2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-0if97e2","updated":"20230723225833"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也是利用现有的电话线路来实现网络连接的目地，只是连接的两端都需要由ISDN 的调制解调器来提供连接功能。ISDN的传输有多种信道可供使用，并且可以将多个信道整合应用，因此速度可以成倍成长。"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-pwln2z2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-pwln2z2","updated":"20230723225837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. 非对称数字用户环路 Asymmetric Digital Subscribe Line ADSL ;使用PPPoE协议"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-r1wr8ei","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-r1wr8ei","updated":"20230723225842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也是通过电话线来拨号后取得IP的一个方法，只不过这个方式使用的是电话的高频部分，与一般的语音电话的频率不同，ADSL同样使用调制解调器，只不过它通过的是PPPoE的方法，将PPP仿真在以太网卡上，因此你的主机需要通过一张网卡来连接到调制解调器，并通过拨接程序来取得新的接口，ppp0."}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-fhytcu0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-fhytcu0","updated":"20230723225807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. 电缆调制解调器 CableModem"}]},{"ID":"20230723225807-b5pfvjv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723225807-b5pfvjv","updated":"20230723225844"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主要通过有线电视使用的缆线作为网络信号介质，同样需要具备调制解调器来连接到ISP，以取得网络参数来上网，Cable Modem 的带宽主要是共享型的，所以通过具有区域性，"}]},{"ID":"20230723225722-n22nfgw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723225722-n22nfgw","updated":"20230723225722"}}]}